				\begin{document}${<}30~\mu\mbox{rad}$\end{document} (6 arcsec) (both 1-sigma) for the two cross-star tracker-bore sight axes. The pointing accuracy about the bore axis is specified to be <120μrad\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
